On Windows:

Go to Task Scheduler
Create Task...
Name the task and check the option "Run with highest privileges"
Choose the OS on the "Configure for" option

Go to Triggers
New...
From "Begin the task" select the "At startup" option
Ok

Go to Actions
New...
Action: Start a program
Select the .pyw script
Ok

Go to Conditions
Uncheck the option "Start the task only if the computer is on AC power"

Ok